# Soul In Forge – Backend Quick Start

## 1. Cài dependencies
npm install

## 2. Cập nhật URI MongoDB tại: config/db.js
mongoose.connect(
  "mongodb+srv://buivobaongochp2005_db_user:tXwtCOac64xFSqTb@cluster0.mongodb.net/SIFgame"
);

## 3. Chạy backend
node server.js

## 4. Kiểm tra server
http://localhost:3000/

## 5. Test Register
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Body:
{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

## 6. Test Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Body:
{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

## 7. Dùng token để test Load Profile
GET http://localhost:3000/user/profile
Header:
Authorization: Bearer <token>

## 8. Dừng server
Ctrl + C
